import sys

N = int(input())

AC = 0
WA = 0
TLE = 0
RE = 0

for i in range(N):
    verdict = sys.stdin.readline().rstrip()

    if verdict == "AC":
        AC += 1
    elif verdict == "WA":
        WA += 1
    elif verdict == "TLE":
        TLE += 1
    else:
        RE += 1

print("AC x " + str(AC))
print("WA x " + str(WA))
print("TLE x " + str(TLE))
print("RE x " + str(RE))
